thread.title: Kylie Irvin
thread.title_full: Ticketmaster Resale reviewed by Kylie Irvin

author: Kylie Irvin
title: Kylie Irvin
text: I found this service so quick and easy to use. Being so close to the date of the concert I wasn't sure I'd be successful, but I managed to score some great seats in my preferred area. The checkout process was very quick and easy and the eTicket was sent straight to my email inbox for printing.
